Description: A pure R implementation of the SAINTexpress scoring engines
    for affinity purification-mass spectrometry data, covering both the
    spectral-count and intensity models, together with validation of SAINT
    input tables. The output mirrors the native SAINTexpress 'list.txt'
    format, so protein-protein interactions can be scored without external
    binaries. The underlying method is described in Teo et al. (2014)
    <doi:10.1016/j.jprot.2013.10.023>.
